      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.nps.gov/places/oyster-bay-new-york.htm"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Sagamore Hill, Theodore Roosevelt’s former home, is a National Historic Site right in Oyster Bay.",
